Class KeywordTextStemmedField

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.atlan.model.fields.AtlanField
      • com.atlan.model.fields.SearchableField
        • com.atlan.model.fields.KeywordTextStemmedField
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IKeywordSearchable, ISearchable, IStemmedSearchable, ITextSearchable
    public class KeywordTextStemmedField
extends SearchableField
implements IKeywordSearchable, ITextSearchable, IStemmedSearchable
    Represents any field in Atlan that can be searched by keyword or text-based search operations, including a stemmed variation of the text analyzers.
